# Email patterns (POSIX ERE) for commits *we* own on this fork.
# Policy (identity + commitlint) only validates these commits in a range.
# Upstream monorepo exports and other third-party history are skipped.
# One pattern per line. # comments and blank lines ignored.

# Victor Software House human commits
@victor-software-house\.com$

# GitHub UI merges / web commits
^noreply@github\.com$

# github-actions[bot] (CI automation commits on this repo)
github-actions\[bot\]@users\.noreply\.github\.com$
